# Project UI / Motion

For UI and design work in this repo:

- Apply personal skill **aaa-frontend-motion** (templates, references, snippets).
- Match existing brand tokens and layout primitives when extending this product.
- Prefer Motion (`motion/react`) for UI; add GSAP/R3F only when the surface needs cinema or 3D.
- Do not regress into generic dashboard card grids on marketing pages.
- Keep motion subtle on dense compliance/ops screens; invest craft on marketing, onboarding, Jarvis, and hero surfaces.
